	measure 'Security Elim Adjustment Title' = ```
			
			VAR maxdate =
			    MAX ( 'Securities GL Txn fact - Elim'[Txn Dt])
			RETURN
			    "Security Elim Adjustment" & ", "
			        & SELECTEDVALUE ( 'Reporting Currency'[Rep In Currency] ) & ", "
			        & SELECTEDVALUE ( Framework[Framework Display] ) & ", "
			        & FORMAT ( maxdate, "dd-mmm-yy" )
			
			```
		lineageTag: 9dd16b1f-c0b0-428e-b980-16c288a994fb

